com.esri.mo2.map.dpy
Interface LayerSource

All Known Subinterfaces:
ImageLayerSource, ServerProxy, WorkspaceLayerSource
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseImageLayerSource, BaseLayerSource, BaseWorkspaceLayerSource, FeatureServer, ImageServer
Deprecated. - the interface has been deprecated, see Content API.

public interface LayerSource

A proxy for a kind of external source, that provides Map Layers that are ready to be added to a Map. You normally get the LayerSource to obtain the Layer details from the external source first, after which you can directly use the Layer object/s.
